{"tid":1037402,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知邊個網可以用 UPC 嚟搵歌手同碟名","createTime":"2019-02-26T02:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T16:05:35.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"075b19f861facd2120b0e8e8d9b7f15081f12794","tid":1037402,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:18:34.000Z","msg":"想搵一個最少可以一次入10個 UPC<br />\n<br />\n試過外國d網唔得，好多都搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n有百幾隻舊jpop碟想睇值幾錢，amazon只係一次入到一個 <br />\n<br />\n淨係想抄低歌手同碟名，逐個入真係嘥時間<br />\n<br />\n☺"},{"pid":"59805411175b8a42d48877349209164b64445cfd","tid":1037402,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:21:19.000Z","msg":"唔知邊個台問先好又唔算買賣但又屬於音樂既野 ☺"},{"pid":"0afc38df7ec2da9f1ec30b45af921c0047070bf2","tid":1037402,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T05:11:40.000Z","msg":"舉個例：<br />\n<br />\nUPC barcode 係 4988005574596<br />\n<br />\n如果用依個英文既就搵唔到：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.barcodelookup.com/4988005574596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barcodelookup.com%2F4988005574596&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=bb81ce6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.barcodelookup.com/4988005574596</a><br />\n<br />\n用 amazon jp 就搵到，不過每次只係入到一個：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/aw/s/ref=nb_sb_noss?k=4988005574596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2Fgp%2Faw%2Fs%2Fref%3Dnb_sb_noss%3Fk%3D4988005574596&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=d95a1939\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/aw/s/ref=nb_sb_noss?k=4988005574596</a>"},{"pid":"5e3be1a963b6c708be53696c6b9fbf272c109f1b","tid":1037402,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:23:48.000Z","msg":"數十聲如果都係冇人知唯有放棄囉 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt